{"tid":1548264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我求求各位公務員再寫聯署信同集會","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T19:06:04.000Z","uid":13388,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"47edd8480fde66349c44c3a1fa4c3907f6e56a8d","tid":1548264,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:25:12.000Z","msg":"當831 同今日勇武手足既事件後<br />\n我覺得除左要打國際線外<br />\n我地自己香港人都要升級<br />\n沖緊涼時 我一直諗點升級？<br />\n<br />\n就係要再展現比香港人 外國人 <br />\n同埋林奠中共呢個恐殘暴權比佢地知道<br />\n我地香港人對林奠你做埋d下三流既行為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對唔接受</span><br />\n同埋要證明比大家睇 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地團結一致</span><br />\n<br />\n我記得612 616 618 之後<br />\n有好多公務員都索聯署信同集會 <br />\n表達對五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n所以當林奠所謂既撤回 同恐殘既軍政府<br />\n有公務員手足發夢被捕<br />\n同埋有傳既打死香港市民同埋輪姦女義士<br />\n<br />\n希望你地再一次話比政府知<br />\n我地絕對唔會屈服<br />\n<br />\n想係度求求各位公務員 出一出一次聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非同勇武要團結<br />\n<br />\n利伸 發夢成日係中排食煙既手足上<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"d5e64c69f8f4e9d52f78cf0c38a2c5aa6eb2d1f6","tid":1548264,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:25:30.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"33543f7e12d463f32dc223d41ae6bf65c8c5bf16","tid":1548264,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"【黃雀行動】勇武是蟬、黑警是螂、和理是雀！停止散播死人恐慌！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548260</a>"},{"pid":"0350b9263b61b2dfbaa99cc69a442e3eb069f3e8","tid":1548264,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"0dd82e74626ab932b1d0ab5ea0954fed8557532d","tid":1548264,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"4c9601c1ccff78e9901f3d0a5ec5faea77555821","tid":1548264,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:30:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18fc4ce1e1167ea436573a7f4351f948f909cfdc","tid":1548264,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22c942bdc843106a5b89a91dd7aacc81febd59fe","tid":1548264,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:42:07.000Z","msg":"我推"},{"pid":"501e805df27059771c40cbd28fe830586869da5e","tid":1548264,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:42:44.000Z","msg":"清算得好勁"},{"pid":"5e24739f260d5b34744fd6fccd68f9510405fe90","tid":1548264,"uid":165649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:47:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7ca0ea8a55b86b29ab9d330ac46c4803b31570d","tid":1548264,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efd0df3e82fd601c24114137809b0022af93bac0","tid":1548264,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b26e3c685ce3ffe17465a4c1913545d369f6469","tid":1548264,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11170d1f800ec33eb6e8f3a979ee02c8b1257c8","tid":1548264,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor